headline: Rail merger no guarantee of growth: Analysts
summary: A mega-merger of railroads would have to reverse a slow years-long market for freight to produce growth touted by Union Pacific and Norfolk Southern, an industry panel said. The post Rail merger no guarantee of growth: Analysts appeared first on FreightWaves.
